libgtkentrymask
---------------

GtkEntryMask is base upon GtkEntry and provides mask filtering on input.

The goal of this version would be inclusion in GTK+ mainline with extremely
simple API and code (to do). The API will be not compatible with the original
version (if needing use libgtkxentrymask).

Devel version.

For testing purpose, the package contains :
 * libgtkentrymask
 * test-gtkentrymask
 * libgtkentrymask-2.0.pc
so it's easy to use this class in any GTK+ 2.0 application.
